{"meta":{"domain":"subjects","kid":"5106","authors":[{"fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre","id":"6"}],"title":"","dates":{"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:23 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:23 UTC"}},"nodes":[{"index":0,"parent_index":-1,"body":"<p class=\"Paragraph\">In Spoken Tibetan, compound verbs are more common than simple verbs (verbs comprising only one syllable). For the most part, compound verbs consist of a noun and a \u201cverbalizer.\u201d Verbalizers (<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0fb1\u0f0b\u0f5a\u0f72\u0f42\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f9f\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f54\u0f0b<\/span>) are verbs that do not convey a specific meaning, or else mean \u201cto do\u201d in a general sense. Compound verbs of this sort generally comprise two or three syllables, but some contain up to five.<\/p><p class=\"Paragraph\">The three basic verbalizers are:<\/p><ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0fb1\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span> \/ <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f42\u0f53\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span> (H) \u201cTo do,\u201d \u201cto act\u201d <\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f62\u0f92\u0fb1\u0f42\u0f0b<\/span> \/ <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f66\u0f90\u0fb1\u0f7c\u0f53\u0f0b<\/span> (H) \u201cTo make\u201d<\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f4f\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span> \/ <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f4f\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f42\u0f53\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span> (H) \u201cTo send,\u201d \u201cto do\u201d<\/li> <\/ul><p class=\"Paragraph\">Other verbalizers (some of them used only rarely) include:<\/p><ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f5f\u0f7c\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo make\u201d <\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f5e\u0f74\u0f0b<\/span> (H) \u201cTo say,\u201d \u201cto take\u201d <\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f5e\u0f7a\u0f66\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo take\u201d <\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f66\u0fb3\u0f44\u0f66\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo lift\u201d <\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f63\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo get up\u201d <\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f60\u0f42\u0fb2\u0f7c\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo go\u201d <\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f64\u0f7c\u0f62\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo let go\u201d <\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f50\u0f7a\u0f56\u0f66\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo be caught,\u201d \u201cto be hit\u201d <\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f60\u0f41\u0f7c\u0f62\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo circulate\u201d<\/li> <\/ul><p class=\"Paragraph\">The choice of verbalizer is determined partly by whether the verb is volitional or non-volitional. The verbalizers <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f64\u0f7c\u0f62\u0f0b<\/span>, <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f60\u0f42\u0fb2\u0f7c\u0f0b<\/span>, <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f63\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span>, and <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f50\u0f7a\u0f56\u0f66\u0f0b<\/span> are used in the formation of non-volitional verbs. Following is a chart of some common volitional and non-volitional forms.<\/p><table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"> <tbody> <tr> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f58\u0f42\u0f7c\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f90\u0f7c\u0f62\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f4f\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u201cTo deceive\u201d<\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f58\u0f42\u0f7c\u0f0b\u0f60\u0f41\u0f7c\u0f62\u0f0b\u0f50\u0f7a\u0f56\u0f66\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"414\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u201cTo be deceived\u201d<\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <tr> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f41\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f41\u0fb2\u0f7c\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f66\u0fb3\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u201cTo make angry\u201d<\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f41\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f41\u0fb2\u0f7c\u0f0b\u0f63\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"414\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u201cTo get angry\u201d<\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <tr> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f61\u0f62\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f92\u0fb1\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f4f\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u201cTo improve\u201d<\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f61\u0f62\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f92\u0fb1\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f60\u0f42\u0fb2\u0f7c\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"414\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u201cTo be improved\u201d<\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <tr> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f58\u0f7a\u0f0b\u0f58\u0f51\u0f60\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f92\u0fb1\u0f42\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u201cTo shoot\u201d<\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f58\u0f7a\u0f0b\u0f58\u0f51\u0f60\u0f0b\u0f50\u0f7a\u0f56\u0f66\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"414\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u201cTo be hit (by a bullet)\u201d<\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <tr> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f58\u0f72\u0f42\u0f0b\u0f46\u0f74\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f4f\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u201cTo shed tears\u201d<\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f58\u0f72\u0f42\u0f0b\u0f46\u0f74\u0f0b\u0f64\u0f7c\u0f62\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"414\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u201cTo burst into tears\u201d<\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <tr> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f62\u0f9f\u0f74\u0f42\u0f0b\u0f51\u0fb2\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f4f\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u201cTo fart (intentionally)\u201d<\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f62\u0f9f\u0f74\u0f42\u0f0b\u0f51\u0fb2\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f64\u0f7c\u0f62\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"414\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u201cTo fart (accidentally)\u201d<\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <tr> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f42\u0f45\u0f72\u0f53\u0f0b\u0f54\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f4f\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u201cTo urinate (intentionally)<\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f42\u0f45\u0f72\u0f53\u0f0b\u0f54\u0f0b\u0f64\u0f7c\u0f62\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"414\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u201cTo wet oneself \u201c<\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <tr> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f66\u0f58\u0f0b\u0f56\u0fb3\u0f7c\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f4f\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u201cTo ponder\u201d<\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f66\u0f58\u0f0b\u0f56\u0fb3\u0f7c\u0f0b\u0f60\u0f41\u0f7c\u0f62\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"414\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u201cTo have an idea\u201d<\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <tr> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f66\u0f90\u0fb1\u0f74\u0f42\u0f0b\u0f54\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f90\u0fb1\u0f74\u0f42\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u201cTo (make oneself) vomit\u201d<\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f66\u0f90\u0fb1\u0f74\u0f42\u0f0b\u0f54\u0f0b\u0f64\u0f7c\u0f62\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"414\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u201cTo vomit\u201d<\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <\/tbody> <\/table><p class=\"Paragraph\">The honorifics of compound verbs are formed by putting both the verbalizer and the preceding noun in the honorific.<\/p><table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"> <tbody> <tr> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f46\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f92\u0fb1\u0f42\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u201cTo marry\u201d<\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f41\u0fb2\u0f74\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f66\u0f90\u0fb1\u0f7c\u0f53\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"414\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u201cTo marry\u201d (H)<\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <tr> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f63\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f40\u0f0b\u0f56\u0fb1\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u201cTo work\u201d<\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f55\u0fb1\u0f42\u0f0b\u0f63\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f42\u0f53\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"414\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">\u201cTo work\u201d (H)<\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <\/tbody> <\/table><p class=\"Paragraph\">Compound verbs retain a certain syntactic flexibility: the noun can be separated from the verbalizer by an adverb or a negation, and may also be marked by a complement:<\/p><ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f66\u0f58\u0f0b\u0f56\u0fb3\u0f7c\u0f0b\u0f58\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f54\u0f7c\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f4f\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f51\u0f42\u0f7c\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0d<\/span> \u201c(We) have to give it a lot of thought.\u201d<\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f74\u0f0b\u0f58\u0f7c\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f42\u0f5e\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f99\u0f53\u0f0b\u0f54\u0f7c\u0f0b\u0f45\u0f72\u0f42\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f4f\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f0d<\/span> \u201cThe girl sang a lovely song.\u201d<\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f42\u0f5f\u0f56\u0f0b\u0f42\u0f5f\u0f56\u0f0b\u0f58\u0f0b\u0f56\u0fb1\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f53\u0f0b\u0f49\u0f7a\u0f53\u0f0b\u0f41\u0f0b\u0f60\u0f51\u0f74\u0f42<\/span> \u201cIf you\u2019re not careful, it\u2019s risky.\u201d<\/li> <\/ul><p class=\"Paragraph\">The semantics of a verb offer no clue to the verbalizer that should be used. As a general rule, compound verbs take only one verbalizer.<\/p><ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f63\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f40\u0f0b\u0f56\u0fb1\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo work\u201d (but not *<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f63\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f40\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f4f\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span> or *<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f63\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f40\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f92\u0fb1\u0f42\u0f0b<\/span>)<\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f46\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f92\u0fb1\u0f42\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo marry\u201d (but not *<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f46\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f56\u0fb1\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span> or *<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f46\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f4f\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span>)<\/li> <\/ul><p class=\"Paragraph\">In certain cases, however, there is a choice of which verbalizer may be used:<\/p><ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f66\u0fa4\u0fb1\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f4f\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span> or <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f66\u0fa4\u0fb1\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f56\u0fb1\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo use\u201d<\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f60\u0f42\u0f74\u0f63\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f90\u0fb1\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f62\u0f92\u0fb1\u0f56\u0f0b<\/span> or <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f60\u0f42\u0f74\u0f63\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f90\u0fb1\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f56\u0fb1\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo move\u201d <\/li> <\/ul><p class=\"Paragraph\">In some exceptional instances, different verbalizers may be used but the overall meaning is different in each case.<\/p><ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f66\u0f90\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f4f\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo call,\u201d but <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f66\u0f90\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f92\u0fb1\u0f42\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo shout\u201d<\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f58\u0f7a\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f92\u0fb1\u0f42\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo set fire,\u201d but <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f58\u0f7a\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f4f\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo light,\u201d \u201cto make a fire\u201d<\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f63\u0f53\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f92\u0fb1\u0f42\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo reply,\u201d but <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f63\u0f53\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f4f\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo send a message\u201d<\/li> <\/ul><p class=\"Paragraph\">Like all verbs, verbalizers must be followed by auxiliaries. Here is a list of the \u201cconjugations\u201d (in all the tense-aspects and moods) of the most common auxiliaries. Knowing all these forms will enable you to conjugate most verbs in Standard Tibetan.<\/p><table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"> <tbody> <tr> <td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Verbalizer <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f4f\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Verbalizer <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f62\u0f92\u0fb1\u0f42\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Verbalizer <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0fb1\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <tr> <td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f4f\u0f44\u0f0b(\u0f42\u0f4f\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f0b)\u0f42\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f61\u0f72\u0f53\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f62\u0f92\u0fb1\u0f42\u0f0b\u0f42\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f61\u0f72\u0f53\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0fb1\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f42\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f61\u0f72\u0f53\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <tr> <td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f4f\u0f44\u0f0b(\u0f42\u0f4f\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f0b)\u0f42\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f62\u0f92\u0fb1\u0f42\u0f0b\u0f42\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f5